    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/7dbe5cb81b9605ae84160aea80970a53.avif?t=1771914238\" width=1232 height=706 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >『连接的线索指向一个真相。』</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《关联线索》是一款充满19世纪古典侦探小说风格的斜45度推理冒险游戏。<br>亲自调查案发现场，收集线索，通过推理揭开隐藏的真相吧！<br>找出隐藏在人群中的犯人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/978bac1e457256ee7d7c4edf1a3495d1.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/978bac1e457256ee7d7c4edf1a3495d1.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/978bac1e457256ee7d7c4edf1a3495d1.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在城市中心发生了一起银行抢劫案。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >犯人抢走了大笔现金和金库里的贵重宝物后逃之夭夭。<br>新人侦探黛安娜将从这起案件开始，挑战无数悬而未决的案件。<br>能否收集证据、识破嫌疑人的谎言，并最终逮捕真凶？<br>案件的结局，完全取决于你的推理力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- 证据收集</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细调查案发现场，利用各种工具发现线索。<br>用放大镜观察细微痕迹，用炭粉提取指纹，通过走访获取嫌疑人的证言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/6f34378a9d2322554bd154ef72b3a1d0.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/6f34378a9d2322554bd154ef72b3a1d0.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/6f34378a9d2322554bd154ef72b3a1d0.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/fc72b0ed1d20b84991ec3c21684b4700.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/fc72b0ed1d20b84991ec3c21684b4700.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/fc72b0ed1d20b84991ec3c21684b4700.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >线索获取 —— 使用工具调查案发现场！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/90a6aa4a13b96e8c96de5d27ec49711c.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/90a6aa4a13b96e8c96de5d27ec49711c.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/90a6aa4a13b96e8c96de5d27ec49711c.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/ad2f99c2af0f546ce9e07318dda5be49.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/ad2f99c2af0f546ce9e07318dda5be49.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/ad2f99c2af0f546ce9e07318dda5be49.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >密码解读 —— 破解密码，发现隐藏的秘密场所！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/c4cb04ba65e6dfe25ae5415ee537d058.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/c4cb04ba65e6dfe25ae5415ee537d058.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/c4cb04ba65e6dfe25ae5415ee537d058.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/6cc7c1f8acc52503319fb75554ed5129.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/6cc7c1f8acc52503319fb75554ed5129.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/6cc7c1f8acc52503319fb75554ed5129.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盘问 —— 出示线索，逼出嫌疑人的证言！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- 动作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >案发现场总是潜藏危险。<br>要在人群中潜入，或通过伪装避开警察的目光，还必须制服顽抗的犯人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/95cee03dad8eddd1001c5c57d3c46180.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/95cee03dad8eddd1001c5c57d3c46180.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/95cee03dad8eddd1001c5c57d3c46180.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/bf19d0361e82f595bf02c52b1c085fe6.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/bf19d0361e82f595bf02c52b1c085fe6.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/bf19d0361e82f595bf02c52b1c085fe6.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入 —— 换装，避开警察的注视！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/00f23e82792607a87d59caa0521647ea.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/00f23e82792607a87d59caa0521647ea.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/00f23e82792607a87d59caa0521647ea.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟踪 &amp; QTE —— 在暗影中追捕嫌疑人！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/9b44e6dd07ac1f453580cba29e0f073d.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/9b44e6dd07ac1f453580cba29e0f073d.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/9b44e6dd07ac1f453580cba29e0f073d.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗 —— 制伏抵抗的恶徒并逮捕！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- 推理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集到的证据可在侦探事务所的「侦探之墙」上进行整理。<br>逐一揭开被害人与犯人的关系、使用的凶器、案件经过，重构事件真相。<br>当所有嫌疑人齐聚一堂时，能否识破谎言并指认最终的犯人，全靠你自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/13ec412f47a28114a400b50cc40f224d.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/13ec412f47a28114a400b50cc40f224d.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/13ec412f47a28114a400b50cc40f224d.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >案件重构 —— 用收集到的线索还原案件经过！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/0b5f083c06da1b2b569eb3f68226a5e4.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/0b5f083c06da1b2b569eb3f68226a5e4.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/0b5f083c06da1b2b569eb3f68226a5e4.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >矛盾推理 —— 识破谎言，指认真正的犯人！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于推理游戏的特性，游戏中还会出现利用音效与色彩的解谜要素。<br>为了让玩家畅快体验，我们加入了多种反馈与辅助功能：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/b368b0026fe2634c1edf4b3f1e83e0f5.poster.avif?t=1771914238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/b368b0026fe2634c1edf4b3f1e83e0f5.webm?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777200/extras/b368b0026fe2634c1edf4b3f1e83e0f5.mp4?t=1771914238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >听觉辅助：将重要音效以视觉特效呈现</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色觉辅助：通过调整明度、饱和度以及文字颜色来辅助辨识</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集证据、审问嫌疑人、揭开案件真相吧！<br>是时候化身为19世纪侦探小说中的主人公，挑战那些尚未解开的悬案了。<br>你的推理，将决定真相。</p>",
